Package jetbrains.mps.generator.impl.query

Class QueryProviderBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • jetbrains.mps.generator.impl.query.QueryProviderBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GeneratorQueryProvider
    public abstract class QueryProviderBase
extends Object
implements GeneratorQueryProvider
    This is a base implementation of GeneratorQueryProvider which generated class with queries shall extend to protect itself from future modifications of the interface.
